callee: SELECT COALESCE(statuses.language, 'und') AS language, count(*) AS value FROM statuses INNER JOIN statuses_tags ON statuses_tags.status_id = statuses.id WHERE statuses_tags.tag_id = NULL AND statuses.id BETWEEN 111350145810432000 AND 111361470431232000 GROUP BY COALESCE(statuses.language, 'und') ORDER BY count(*) DESC LIMIT 10
